OL,3,CWitnesses sought after rape and
OL,4,Crobbery at nature reserve
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for witnesses and
OL,7,Fdash-cam footage following reports of
OL,8,Fa rape and robbery at a nature reserve
OL,9,Fin West Berkshire.
OL,11,FThames Valley Police said they
OL,12,Freceived a report that a man in his
OL,13,F20's was assaulted by an unknown man
OL,14,Fin the car park of Padworth Common
OL,15,FNature Reserve.
OL,17,FThe attack happened at around 6.30pm
OL,18,Fon Thursday, 9th July.
OL,20,FDuring the offence, the offender stole
OL,21,F#50 from the victim's pocket.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
