OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783855166
OL,3,CWitnesses sought after rape and
OL,4,Crobbery at nature reserve
OL,6,F"Since the rape was reported to us, we
OL,7,Fhave been carrying out a number of
OL,8,Fenquiries to establish exactly what
OL,9,Fhappened and identify the offender. As
OL,10,Fpart of that ongoing investigation, we
OL,11,Fare now appealing to the public for
OL,12,Finformation that may assist us.
OL,14,F"I would like to hear from anyone who
OL,15,Fmay have seen this incident or part of
OL,16,Fthe incident as it unfolded. We are
OL,17,Fparticularly keen to hear from
OL,18,Fmotorists with dash-cam footage
OL,19,Frecorded in the area around the time
OL,20,Fof the offence, as this may assist our
OL,21,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
