OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783855166
OL,3,CWitnesses sought after rape and
OL,4,Crobbery at nature reserve
OL,6,F"Officers are keen to speak to anyone
OL,7,Fwho may have seen a red vehicle in the
OL,8,Farea at the time of the incident.
OL,10,F"You will see an increased police
OL,11,Fpresence in the area over the coming
OL,12,Fdays as we continue our enquiries,
OL,13,Fprovide reassurance to the community
OL,14,Fand help keep people safe.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
